===Noun===
'''토착어''' to-chag-eo (hanja: [[土着語]])
#the native language of a region; a regional language; a regional dialect
#:제주도는 지리적 여건으로 말미암아 한국어의 특수한 '''토착어'''를 형성하였다. (''Jejudo-neun jirijeok yeogeon-euro malmiama Hangugeo-ui teuksuhan '''tochageo'''-reul hyeongseong hayeottda.'')  Due to its geographic situation, Cheju Island developed a unique '''regional dialect''' of Korean.

